    'White Lotus ‚Äì Home of Sanctuaries',
    'White Lotus ‚Äì Home of Sanctuaries',
    'White Lotus ‚Äì Home of Sanctuaries is a thoughtfully crafted luxury villa development located along the serene IVC Road in North Bengaluru. Spread across 14 acres with just 95 homes (‚âà7 homes per acre), this low-density community is designed as a haven where residents can reconnect with nature without compromising on modern luxury.

